import React from 'react';

const Form = ({submitFn}) => {
    <form
        onSubmit={submitFn}>
        <imput 
            name="name"
        />
        <imput 
            name="link"
        />
        <imput 
            name="image"
        />
        <textarea 
            name="description"
        />
    </form>
}

export default Form;
